---
import '../../styles/global.css';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>App Popular · Wilbert Veloz</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body class="bg-[#0f0e0c] text-[#e8e0d0] font-sans">

  <Nav />

  <section class="px-10 pt-16 pb-8 max-w-3xl">
    <a href="/work" class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-white/30 hover:text-[#c9873a] transition-colors mb-8 inline-block">← All projects</a>
    <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[#c9873a] mb-3">Banco Popular Dominicano · 2023 – Present</p>
    <h1 class="font-display text-6xl font-normal text-[#e8e0d0] mb-2">App Popular</h1>
    <p class="font-display text-2xl italic text-[#c9873a] font-normal mb-8">Financial · iOS & Android · Tech Lead</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-10">
      <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#e8e0d0]/40 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">SwiftUI</span>
      <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#e8e0d0]/40 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Kotlin</span>
      <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#e8e0d0]/40 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">iOS</span>
      <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#e8e0d0]/40 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Android</span>
      <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#e8e0d0]/40 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Agile</span>
      <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-[#e8e0d0]/40 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">CI/CD</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="border-white/8 mx-10 mb-12" />

  <section class="px-10 pb-20 max-w-3xl">

    <div class="mb-10">
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[#c9873a] mb-4">Overview</p>
      <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.9] text-white/60 font-light mb-4">App Popular is Banco Popular Dominicano's flagship mobile app — one of the most widely used banking platforms in the Dominican Republic. The app gives clients full control of their finances from their phone, eliminating the need to visit a branch for everyday banking needs.</p>
      <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.9] text-white/60 font-light">Clients can check balances, move money, make every type of transaction and reclamation, and manage their account configurations — all through a secure, stable mobile experience on both iOS and Android.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-10">
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[#c9873a] mb-4">My Role</p>
      <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.9] text-white/60 font-light mb-4">As Tech Lead of an Agile team, I'm involved in the full software lifecycle of every feature we ship. My responsibilities span from the earliest planning stages through to production deployment.</p>
      <div class="space-y-3 mt-4">
        <div class="flex gap-4"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a] flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></span><p class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light leading-relaxed">Define and scope features based on product and business needs, producing technical documentation that minimizes risk before development begins.</p></div>
        <div class="flex gap-4"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a] flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></span><p class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light leading-relaxed">Design the data architecture required for each feature, aligned with client needs and backend capabilities.</p></div>
        <div class="flex gap-4"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a] flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></span><p class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light leading-relaxed">Participate in UX/UI decisions based on current backend structure, ensuring what gets designed can actually be built.</p></div>
        <div class="flex gap-4"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a] flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></span><p class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light leading-relaxed">Track features from conception through backend service readiness, with all security controls the institution requires in place.</p></div>
        <div class="flex gap-4"><span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-[#c9873a] flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></span><p class="text-sm text-white/50 font-light leading-relaxed">Own deployment across Development, QA, and Production environments — ensuring stability at every stage before reaching clients.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-10">
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase text-[#c9873a] mb-4">Featured — Toke</p>
      <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.9] text-white/60 font-light">Toke is a payment infrastructure feature launched within App Popular to transform financial inclusion across the Dominican Republic. I contributed to the architecture design, security controls, and the full deployment pipeline that brought it to production.</p>
    </div>

  </section>

  <footer class="px-10 py-8 border-t border-white/6 flex justify-between items-center">
    <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-white/20">Wilbert Veloz · Santo Domingo, DR</span>
    <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-white/20">2025</span>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>